<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.5.4">
<l>ūrāṉ kuṭantai yuttamaṉo rukā lirukāl cilaivaḷaiya</l>
<l>tērā varakkar tērveḷḷañ ceṟṟāṉ vaṟṟā varupuṉalcūḻ</l>
<l>pērāṉ pērā yiramuṭaiyāṉ piṟaṅku ciṟaivaṇ ṭaṟaikiṉṟa</l>
<l>tārāṉ ṟārā vayalcūḻnta cāḷak kirāma maṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Heart, take refuge in Śālagrāma encircled by paddy fields with herons</l>
<l rend="indent">of him of Ūr, the supreme in Kuṭantai,</l>
<l>The one who destroyed the flood of chariots of the unwitting demons</l>
<l rend="indent">when [he] bent the two ends of a bow one time,</l>
<l>The one of Pēr encircled by flowing waters that never dry,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one with one-thousand names,</l>
<l>The one with a garland where hum bees with glistening wings.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
